title: Rush - R30: 30th Anniversary World Tour (2 CD) mp3
description:
Info

Released: 22 November 2005
Recorded: 24 September 2004 at the Festhalle Frankfurt
Genre: Hard rock, progressive rock
Label: Anthem, Atlantic

The R30 Deluxe Edition 2 DVD & 2 CD set features Rush's Frankfurt, Germany concert in September 2004 near the close of their 30th Anniversary World Tour. Songs include the exclusive "R30 Overture" (an instrumental medley of "Finding My Way," "Anthem," "Bastille Day," "A Passage To Bangkok," "Cygnus X-1," and "Hemispheres), "Xanadu," "Subdivisions," "Red Barchetta," "Summertime Blues" (from last year's covers EP Feedback), and the "vault" track "Between The Wheels" which hasn't been performed live in 20 years.
